{"tid":970122,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"香港航空微博指出：對制造謠言者進行法律行動","createTime":"2019-01-05T14:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T16:29:36.000Z","uid":2161,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"c1cf62d97377c7cff1dbecae06c8efc098afc97a","tid":970122,"uid":2161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T14:35:21.000Z","msg":"近日有高層相繼離職的香港航空，陷入財困結業傳聞。香港航空在微博表示，港航如常營運，並致力為選擇乘搭的客戶提供最優質服務，保留對毫無根據製造謠言者採取法律行動的權利。<br />\n香港航空指，去年12月21日至31日假期高峰期間，香港航空營運超過1,200航班，運載近25萬人次。2018年對於香港航空而言是豐收的一年，除了達成超過764萬人次載客量，全年收益更預計超出目標。公司衷心感謝客戶和業務合作夥伴持續的信任及支持。                       <br />\n香港航空強調，重視與服務供貨商的良好合作關係，並持續保持良好溝通。香港航空與藍十字（亞太）保險公司並沒有業務合作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d8VESs4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd8VESs4.png&h=0efb572b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dac2ccaa43cc9ed7c5ed0f7aeee8832c210bc79e","tid":970122,"uid":2161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T14:36:17.000Z","msg":"買咗hx既唔洗驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05db0c42fb66d520efea668073fcc842f498e26a","tid":970122,"uid":2161,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T14:40:50.000Z","msg":"有冇朋友定返啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e625f775b8fbd65884e95552c9c2561e44828b","tid":970122,"uid":176442,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T14:45:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/22/124517_84947975a6fb34652d325a36bca00af3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F22%2F124517_84947975a6fb34652d325a36bca00af3.gif&h=332d8557&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b18e0a21ee9d45058c2c0540b30977f9fe73dda","tid":970122,"uid":20658,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"05db0c42fb66d520efea668073fcc842f498e26a","tid":970122,"uid":2161,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"r